# Cursor Agent Installation Prompt

Copy this entire prompt and paste it into your Cursor Agent chat. It installs **all** recommended skills, rules, and references in one step — no separate SKILSS.json download needed.

---

## Prompt for Cursor/Claude:

"Hey! Please install the following AI agent skills and rules into this workspace.

Also, please always adhere to the following rules for all subsequent work in this session:

# The Optimized Agent Workflow
ALWAYS start with a \"Scope Prompt\" for new features:
1. Identify ONLY required files.
2. Do NOT scan the full repo.
3. Ask before opening more than 5 files.
4. Create an implementation plan first.
5. Wait for user approval.

# Force \"Plan → Build → Fix\" Phases
- Phase 1 (Planning): Only create architecture plan. No code. List files needed.
- Phase 2 (Targeted Build): Implement ONLY based on approved plan. Touch only listed files.
- Phase 3 (Fix): Fix only the specific bug. Do not reanalyze the whole system.

Execute these commands in the terminal sequentially. Use `.git` repository URLs (not web links). Run `npx skills add <repo> --list` first if a skill name is unknown.

```bash
# ── Core Recommended Skills (30-pack) ──────────────────────────────────────

# Vercel Agent Skills
npx skills add https://github.com/vercel-labs/agent-skills.git --skill vercel-react-best-practices -y
npx skills add https://github.com/vercel-labs/agent-skills.git --skill web-design-guidelines -y
npx skills add https://github.com/vercel-labs/agent-skills.git --skill vercel-composition-patterns -y
npx skills add https://github.com/vercel-labs/agent-skills.git --skill vercel-react-view-transitions -y

# Awesome Cursor Skills (spencerpauly)
npx skills add https://github.com/spencerpauly/awesome-cursor-skills.git --skill react-native-patterns -y
npx skills add https://github.com/spencerpauly/awesome-cursor-skills.git --skill architecture-decision-records -y
npx skills add https://github.com/spencerpauly/awesome-cursor-skills.git --skill database-design -y

# Matt Pocock — Planning & Architecture
npx skills add https://github.com/mattpocock/skills.git --skill to-issues -y
npx skills add https://github.com/mattpocock/skills.git --skill improve-codebase-architecture -y

# Cursor Skills (aussiegingersnap)
npx skills add https://github.com/aussiegingersnap/cursor-skills.git --skill nextjs-16 -y
npx skills add https://github.com/aussiegingersnap/cursor-skills.git --skill ui-design-system -y
npx skills add https://github.com/aussiegingersnap/cursor-skills.git --skill ui-principles -y
npx skills add https://github.com/aussiegingersnap/cursor-skills.git --skill state-tanstack -y
npx skills add https://github.com/aussiegingersnap/cursor-skills.git --skill db-postgres -y
npx skills add https://github.com/aussiegingersnap/cursor-skills.git --skill api-rest -y
npx skills add https://github.com/aussiegingersnap/cursor-skills.git --skill auth-better-auth -y

# Next.js & Supabase Cursor Rules (project-local — do NOT use mdskills install; it overwrites .cursorrules)
# Rules live in .cursor/rules/*.mdc and are already committed for this workspace:
#   .cursor/rules/cursor-nextjs.mdc
#   .cursor/rules/cursor-nextjs-typescript-tailwind.mdc
#   .cursor/rules/cursor-typescript-nextjs-supabase.mdc
#   .cursor/rules/cursor-nextjs-vercel-supabase.mdc
# Keep BA Copilot context in .cursorrules only.

# Mindrally — Next.js + Tailwind + Supabase
npx skills add https://github.com/mindrally/skills.git --skill nextjs-typescript-tailwindcss-supabase -y

# shadcn Improve + Supastarter
npx skills add https://github.com/shadcn/improve.git --skill improve -y
npx skills add https://github.com/oscardrt/supastarter-nextjs-skill.git -y

# AbsolutelySkilled Registry (OWASP, Auth, Clean Code, System Design, A11y, Design Systems)
npx skills add https://github.com/AbsolutelySkilled/AbsolutelySkilled.git --skill absolute -y

# ── Workspace & Utility Skills ───────────────────────────────────────────────

npx skills add https://github.com/vercel-labs/skills.git --skill find-skills -y
npx skills add https://github.com/gashiartim/ux-enhancer.git -y
npx skills add https://github.com/Agents365-ai/drawio-skill.git --skill drawio-skill -y
npx skills add https://github.com/DietrichGebert/ponytail.git --skill ponytail -y

# ── Architecture ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

npx skills add https://github.com/ciembor/agent-rules-books.git --skill agent-rules-books -y
npx skills add https://github.com/wshobson/agents.git --skill agents-marketplace -y

# ── Next.js ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

npx skills add https://github.com/vercel/ai.git --skill vercel-ai-sdk-rules -y
npx skills add https://github.com/ixartz/Next-js-Boilerplate.git --skill next-js-saas-boilerplate-rules -y

# ── React ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

npx skills add https://github.com/kentcdodds/react-patterns.git --skill react-patterns -y
npx skills add https://github.com/alan2207/bulletproof-react.git --skill bulletproof-react -y

# ── TypeScript ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

npx skills add https://github.com/total-typescript/total-typescript-book.git --skill typescript-expert -y
npx skills add https://github.com/type-challenges/type-challenges.git --skill type-challenges -y

# ── Supabase ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

npx skills add https://github.com/supabase/supabase.git --skill supabase-official -y
npx skills add https://github.com/supabase/ui.git --skill supabase-ui -y
npx skills add https://github.com/supabase/supabase.git --skill supabase-examples -y

# ── Stripe ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

npx skills add https://github.com/stripe-samples/stripe-samples.git --skill stripe-samples -y
npx skills add https://github.com/vercel/nextjs-subscription-payments.git --skill next-js-stripe-starter -y
npx skills add https://github.com/nextacular/nextacular.git --skill saas-starter-stripe -y

# ── Tailwind v4 ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

npx skills add https://github.com/tailwindlabs/tailwindcss.git --skill tailwind-css -y
npx skills add https://github.com/tailwindlabs/tailwindcss-forms.git --skill tailwind-plus-patterns -y
npx skills add https://github.com/bitjaru/styleseed.git --skill styleseed -y

# ── shadcn/ui ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

npx skills add https://github.com/shadcn-ui/ui.git --skill shadcn -y
npx skills add https://github.com/majiayu000/claude-skill-registry.git --skill nextjs-shadcn-skill -y

# ── UI/UX ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

npx skills add https://github.com/refactoringui/refactoringui-book.git --skill refactoring-ui -y
npx skills add https://github.com/shadcnblocks/aceternity-ui.git --skill aceternity-ui -y
npx skills add https://github.com/magicuidesign/magicui.git --skill magic-ui -y
npx skills add https://github.com/origin-space/originui.git --skill origin-ui -y
npx skills add https://github.com/tremorlabs/tremor.git --skill tremor -y
npx skills add https://github.com/cschroeter/park-ui.git --skill park-ui -y
npx skills add https://github.com/markmead/hyperui.git --skill hyperui -y
npx skills add https://github.com/themesberg/flowbite.git --skill flowbite -y
npx skills add https://github.com/heroui-inc/heroui.git --skill heroui -y

# ── Accessibility ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

npx skills add https://github.com/adobe/react-spectrum.git --skill react-aria -y
npx skills add https://github.com/dequelabs/axe-core.git --skill axe-core -y
npx skills add https://github.com/storybookjs/storybook.git --skill storybook-a11y -y

# ── User Testing ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

npx skills add https://github.com/microsoft/playwright.git --skill playwright -y
npx skills add https://github.com/cypress-io/cypress.git --skill cypress -y
npx skills add https://github.com/testing-library/react-testing-library.git --skill testing-library -y

# ── Security ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

npx skills add https://github.com/OWASP/CheatSheetSeries.git --skill owasp-cheat-sheets -y
npx skills add https://github.com/semgrep/semgrep.git --skill semgrep -y
npx skills add https://github.com/colinhacks/zod.git --skill zod-validation -y
npx skills add https://github.com/nextauthjs/next-auth.git --skill auth-js -y
npx skills add https://github.com/better-auth/better-auth.git --skill better-auth -y
npx skills add https://github.com/arcjet/arcjet-js.git --skill arcjet -y

# ── Database ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

npx skills add https://github.com/drizzle-team/drizzle-orm.git --skill drizzle-orm -y
npx skills add https://github.com/prisma/prisma.git --skill prisma -y
npx skills add https://github.com/eugene-khyst/postgresql-performance-essentials.git --skill postgresql-patterns -y

# ── Messaging ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

npx skills add https://github.com/triggerdotdev/trigger.dev.git --skill trigger-dev -y
npx skills add https://github.com/novuhq/novu.git --skill novu -y

# ── DevOps ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

npx skills add https://github.com/vercel/turborepo.git --skill turborepo -y
npx skills add https://github.com/coollabsio/coolify.git --skill coolify -y
npx skills add https://github.com/Dokploy/dokploy.git --skill dokploy -y

# ── MCP Servers ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

npx skills add https://github.com/upstash/context7.git --skill context7-mcp --skill context7-cli --skill find-docs -y
# Note: firecrawl, modelcontextprotocol/servers, github-mcp-server, playwright-mcp are MCP servers — install via Cursor MCP settings, not npx skills

# ── SkillSpector Test Fixtures (Nvidia — security testing) ─────────────────

npx skills add https://github.com/nvidia/skillspector.git --skill chef-assistant -y
npx skills add https://github.com/nvidia/skillspector.git --skill code-formatter -y
npx skills add https://github.com/nvidia/skillspector.git --skill friendly-greeter -y
